{"tid":1290243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊再度榮膺MVP，一齊細數警隊光輝時刻！","createTime":"2019-07-06T12:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T23:46:45.000Z","uid":13754,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe107c3f0634c4a7518373d443f8e63fed743761","tid":1290243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:07:17.000Z","msg":"2014年 928 戴耀廷喺深夜宣佈佔中正式啟動，但啲人聽到之後走嘅走，係警方喺夏慤道放催淚彈，協助佔中成事！<br />\n2016年 新年流流走去搞啲小販令到旺角起義<br />\n2019年 612放催淚彈，向示威者開槍，激發二百萬市民大遊行同埋兩次圍警總事件<br />\n2019年 627圍警總，灰衫幫辦親身帶領示威者進攻警總<br />\n2019年 71突然棄守立法會，令示威者可以佔領立法會宣讀宣言<br />\n2019年 屯公保護流鶑同埋嫖客...<br />\n<br />\n就咁計今年內短短兩個月已經有四次MVP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警隊係果然係人類嘅好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c548ae76f9603cf9c919bfb01f8c0409a2bd095a","tid":1290243,"uid":21002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"豬到仆街既隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20f45a787f26d9262eb87828d55be080afdd229","tid":1290243,"uid":53062,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:11:05.000Z","msg":"但係只有朱sir同七警坐監<br />\n幾百個市民判監"},{"pid":"b42163ea61a88195e581aae21678b25ce754cd3a","tid":1290243,"uid":163938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"[7/7活動]第三條戰線正式啟動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1280909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1280909</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4uHDMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4uHDMC.png&h=ffd6339e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HyE09Th.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2